::Aerotaur::
       He rocks Elita in his arms to calm her down a bit before laying her 
back in her crib.  "Actually, sir, yes.  Watch the baby, I have another place 
to be."  He runs out of the room and back down the hall where he had last 
seen Flicker and Nightlight.  On the way he opens a comlink to Kup.  "Sir, 
this is Aerotaur, any idea where they are right now?"

--part1_1e1.55e5b3d.2bb3d485_boundary
